main event: A white round object was sighted in Corpus Christi, Texas, on August 27, 1965.
interesting points: The object was described as round and the size of a dime at arm's length,The object glowed white when observed,The sighting lasted approximately one minute,The object was moving to the northeast when it disappeared,There was no physical evidence found related to the sighting.
witness description: The observer was in the backyard of a brother's home.
